summary: the closer we get to captain marvel movie getting released the more i realize this fandom is gonna hate her. a powerful, cocky...
question: the closer we get to captain marvel movie getting released the more i realize this fandom is gonna hate her. a powerful, cocky and arrogant superhero, who is a female??? and who is become the face of the mcu??? and she isnt tony????
answer:
I’ve aready seen some people hate on her, on instagram mainly, they’re basically afraid she’s gonna steal the show. I personaly can’t wait to see her kick some asses ! Please, people, at leat wait til’ her solo movie is out before judging the character ! This is so petty and ridiculous

And after Feige said she was gonna be the most powerful character introduced in the MCU, men all over the globe began whining because god forbid a woman can be more powerful than a man …

As for tony fans, I can’t talk for all of them. But I’ve already seen some people criticize her because of something a marvel writer said, he compared Carol to Steve, said they were pretty alike in personality. They didn’t need much more to start saying they weren’t gonna like her much if she was like him.

marvel character posters  → carol danvers / captain marvel - requested by anon
“My name is Captain Marvel. I am an Earthling and an Avenger. But today I stand as one with the settlers of Torfa, who claim this planet and its resources as they were freely given in the aftermath of the Behemoth disaster. They are a peaceful people, but I am a woman of war. If you move against them, you move against me. I am willing to die here today, for this cause. I have made my choice. Now you make yours.”
